\c 37
\s Ukukhululwa kwelizwe lakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi inkosi uHezekhiya isi\add ku\add*zwile, yadabula izigqoko zayo, yazembesa ngesaka, yangena endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 2 Yasithuma uEliyakhimi umphathi wendlu, loShebina umabhalane, labadala babapristi bembethe amasaka, kuIsaya umprofethi indodana kaAmozi\x + 37.21. 1.1.\x*.
\v 3 Basebesithi kuye: Utsho njalo uHezekhiya: Lolusuku lusuku lohlupho\x + 22.5.\x* lolokusolwa lolokweyiswa, ngoba abantwana sebefikile emlonyeni wesizalo\x + Hos. 13.13.\x*, kanti akulamandla okubeletha.
\v 4 Mhlawumbe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wakho, izawezwa amazwi kaRabi-Shake, onkosi yeAsiriya, inkosi yakhe, emthume ukuthuka uNkulunkulu ophilayo, lokusola ngamazwi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ewazwileyo. Ngakho phakamisa umkhuleko ngensali etholakeleyo\x + 37.32.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho inceku zenkosi uHezekhiya zafika kuIsaya.
\p
\v 6 UIsaya wasesithi kuzo: Lizakutsho njalo enkosini yenu: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ungesabi amazwi owezwileyo, inceku zenkosi yeAsiriya ezingithuke ngawo.
\v 7 Khangela, ngizafaka umoya kuyo, njalo izakuzwa ihungahunga\x + Jer. 51.46. Obad. 1.1.\x*, ibuyele elizweni layo; njalo ngizayenza ukuthi iwe ngenkemba elizweni layo.
\p
\v 8 URabi-Shake wasebuyela, wafica inkosi yeAsiriya isilwa imelene leLibhina; ngoba wayezwile ukuthi isisukile eLakishi.
\v 9 Wasesizwa ngoTirihaka inkosi yeEthiyophiya\x + 20.5.\x* kuthiwa: Uphumile uku\add za\add*kulwa lawe. Esekuzwile wathuma izithunywa kuHezekhiya esithi:
\v 10 Lizakhuluma kanje kuHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda lithi: UNkulunkulu wakho othembele kuye kangakukhohlisi esithi: IJerusalema kayiyikunikelwa esandleni senkosi yeAsiriya.
\v 11 Khangela, wena usuzwile ukuthi amakhosi eAsiriya enzeni kuwo wonke amazwe ngokuwatshabalalisa. Wena-ke uzakhululwa yini?
\v 12 Onkulunkulu bezizwe bazikhulula yini obaba abazichithayo, iGozani leHarani leRezefi, labantwana beEdeni ababeseTelasari?
\v 13 Ingaphi inkosi yeHamathi\x + Jer. 49.23.\x*, lenkosi yeArpadi\x + Jer. 49.23.\x*, lenkosi yomuzi weSefavayimi, iHena, leIva?
\p
\v 14 UHezekhiya wasesemukela izincwadi esandleni sezithunywa, wazifunda, wenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*; uHezekhiya wasezichaya phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 15 UHezekhiya wasekhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, esithi:
\v 16 N\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ohlala \add phakathi\add* \w kwamakherubhi\w**, nguwe wedwa onguNkulunkulu wayo yonke imibuso yomhlaba; wena wenze amazulu lomhlaba\x + Seb. 4.24.\x*.
\v 17 Thoba indlebe yakho, N\nd kosi\nd*, uzwe\x + Seb. 4.49.\x*, vula amehlo akho, N\nd kosi\nd*, ubone; uzwe wonke amazwi kaSenakheribi awathumele ukuklolodela uNkulunkulu ophilayo.
\v 18 Qiniso, N\nd kosi\nd*, amakhosi eAsiriya achithile zonke izizwe lamazwe azo;
\v 19 aphosela onkulunkulu bazo emlilweni, ngoba babengeyisibo onkulunkulu, kodwa umsebenzi wezandla zabantu, izigodo lamatshe; ngalokho bababhubhisa.
\v 20 Ngakho-ke, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wethu, sisindise esandleni sakhe, ukuze yonke imibuso yomhlaba\x + 45.6.\x* yazi ukuthi wena wedwa uyiN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 21 UIsaya indodana kaAmozi\x + 37.21. 1.1.\x* wasethumela kuHezekhiya, esithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Lokho okukhuleke kimi ngoSenakheribi inkosi yeAsiriya,
\v 22 leli yilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* elikhulume ngaye: Intombi emsulwa, indodakazi yeZiyoni\x + 10.32. Zek. 2.10. 9.9.\x* iyakudelela, iyakuklolodela; indodakazi yeJerusalema inikina ikhanda ngemva kwakho.
\v 23 Ngubani omeyisileyo wamhlambaza? Njalo uphakamisele bani ilizwi, waphakamisela amehlo akho phezulu? Umelene loNgcwele kaIsrayeli.
\v 24 Uklolodele iNkosi ngesandla sezinceku zakho, wathi: Ngobunengi bezinqola zami mina ngenyukele endaweni ephakemeyo yezintaba, ezinhlangothini zeLebhanoni. Njalo ngizagamula imisedari\x + 14.8.\x* yayo emide, ikhethelo lezihlahla zamafiri ayo\x + 14.8.\x*, ngingene ekuphakameni kwemingcele yayo, igusu leKharmeli layo\x + Mika 7.14.\x*.
\v 25 Mina ngagebha, nganatha amanzi, langengaphansi yenyawo zami ngomisa yonke imifula\x + 19.6.\x* yendawo evinjelweyo\x + 19.6.\x*.
\v 26 Kawuzwanga yini ukuthi ngakwenza endulo\x + 10.5,15. 22.11.\x*, ngakubumba\x + 10.5,15. 22.11.\x* ensukwini zendulo? Khathesi ngikufikisile, ukuthi ube ngowokudiliza imizi evikelweyo\x + 25.2.\x* ibe zinqumbi zamanxiwa.
\v 27 Ngakho abahlali bayo babelesandla esifitshane, besaba, baba lenhloni\x + 20.5.\x*, baba \add njeng\add*otshani beganga, lemibhida eluhlaza, utshani bempahla, lamabele ahanguliweyo engakami.
\v 28 Kodwa ngiyakwazi ukuhlala kwakho, lokuphuma kwakho, lokungena kwakho, lokungithukuthelela kwakho.
\v 29 Ngenxa yokungithukuthelela kwakho, lokuthi umsindo\x + Amos 6.1.\x* wakho wenyukele endlebeni zami, ngizakufaka umkhala wami emakhaleni akho, letomu lami endebeni zakho\x + Hlab. 32.9.\x*, ngikwenze ubuyele ngendlela oweza ngayo.
\p
\v 30 Lokhu-ke kuzakuba yisibonakaliso kuwe; lonyaka uzakudla okuzikhulelayo; langomnyaka wesibili umkhukhuzela; kuthi ngomnyaka wesithathu\x + 20.3.\x* lihlanyele, livune, lihlanyele izivini, lidle izithelo zazo.
\v 31 Lokuphephileyo kwendlu yakoJuda okuseleyo kuzaphinda kugxumeke impande phansi, kuthele izithelo ngaphezulu\x + 27.6.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba kuzaphuma eJerusalema insali\x + 37.4.\x*, lokuphephileyo entabeni yeZiyoni. Ukutshiseka kweN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla kuzakwenza lokhu.
\p
\v 33 Ngakho, utsho njalo uJehova ngenkosi yeAsiriya: Kayiyikungena kulumuzi\x + 33.20.\x*, kayiyikutshoka umtshoko khona\x + Hlab. 76.3.\x*, kayiyikuza phambi kwawo \add ile\add*sihlangu, kayiyikubuthelela idundulu maqondana lawo\x + Luka 19.43.\x*.
\v 34 Ngendlela eyeza ngayo, ngayo izabuyela, njalo kayiyikungena kulo umuzi, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 35 Ngoba ngizawuvikela lumuzi ukuwusindisa\x + 38.6.\x*, ngenxa yami, langenxa kaDavida inceku yami.
\p
\v 36 Khona kwaphuma ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\x + 2 Kho. 19.35.\x*\nd*, yatshaya enkambeni yamaAsiriya\x + 14.25. 17.14. 30.31. 31.8. Hlab. 76.6.\x* abazinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lanhlanu. Kwathi bevuka ekuseni kakhulu, khangela-ke, bonke babeyizidumbu ezifileyo.
\p
\v 37 Ngakho uSenakheribi inkosi yeAsiriya wasuka, wahamba ebuyela, wahlala eNineve\x + 31.9.\x*.
\v 38 Kwasekusithi ekhonza endlini kaNisiroki unkulunkulu wakhe, oAdrameleki loSharezeri amadodana akhe bamtshaya ngenkemba; bona basebephephela elizweni leArarathi. UEsarihadoni indodana yakhe wasebusa esikhundleni sakhe.
